# Xcode
#
# gitignore contributors: remember to update Global/Xcode.gitignore, Objective-C.gitignore & Swift.gitignore

## User settings
xcuserdata/

## Package Managers
### Swift Package Manager
.build/
.build-local/
.build-test/
.swiftpm/

### CocoaPods
#
# We recommend against adding the Pods directory to your repository. However, if you'd like to include it,
# then you can uncomment the following line.
# Pods/

### Carthage
#
# We recommend against adding the Carthage/Build directory to your repository. However, if you'd like to include it,
# then you can uncomment the following line.
# Carthage/Build

### Accio
bin/apple_libraries

